Use 'sdg-docs' to browse documentation from all installed modules
Use 'tldrtui' (SUPER+H) to look up command examples with tldr
Use 'helptui' (SUPER+SHIFT+H) to browse the legacy help topics
Use 'document' (SUPER+SHIFT+M) to open external documentation links
Use 'reference' (SUPER+SHIFT+/) to browse config reference sheets
Use 'colortui' to preview the current Material You colour palette
Use 'projects' (SUPER+SHIFT+P) to quickly open projects in your editor
